sentences: Birgit Havenstein (born 4 January 1954) is a German flautist and composer.
At the 1988 Sommerliche Musiktage Hitzacker she won awards for her Graffiti for flute, cello and harp.
Even the earth gave his secrets for violin, alto sax and piano, 1992
Music on an absent cellist for solo harp, 1993
Graffiti for flute, cello and harp, 1988
